Privacy Policy
This privacy policy covers this website ("donutgames.com") and the software distributed by Donut Games ("our Apps"), that are offered on various app markets ("App Markets"), including but not limited to Apple's App Store, Google Play Store and Windows Store.
Donut Games is a trade name owned by Swedish Game Development AB, a registered Swedish company.
Donut Games respects your privacy and is committed to protect any personally identifiable information ("Personal Data") you share with us.
The Personal Data will be used solely by us and the required party or parties, e.g. our ecommerce partner, to fulfill the requested task, and your Personal Data will not be shared with anyone except as described in this Privacy Policy.
If you choose to use this website or our apps ("our Services"), then you agree to this policy. If you don't agree, then close this website and uninstall our Apps.
How Data Is Handled
When purchasing any of our Apps, your Personal Data and payment will be handled by one of the established App Markets.
	Links to their respective privacy policies can be found further down on this page.
Our Apps may download data from donutgames.com from time to time, to provide you with relevant information.
	We do NOT upload any Personal Data in connection with these downloads. The downloads are small, usually less than 0.5 megabytes, and are always related to our own apps and products.
	If you want to turn off this feature, you can click the "options" button in the app and turn off "online features."
Some Apps may contain ads from Google. In those cases, it will be clearly stated on the product page inside the App Market.
	The privacy policy related to Google's ads can be found in a link below.
Our Android Apps use Google Play Services.
* Google Ads Policy:
https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads
* Google Privacy & Terms:
https://policies.google.com/privacy
* Apple Privacy Policy:
https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy
* Microsoft Privacy Policy:
https://privacy.microsoft.com
Cookies
This website uses cookies (small files that our website sends to your browser) to remember which version of the site you choose to use, i.e. mobile or desktop version.
Some pages on this website may also contain links to Zazzle, Facebook and Twitter, which may send cookies to your browser.
Links to the privacy policy of the mentioned companies can be found below:
* Zazzle:
https://www.zazzle.com/mk/policy/privacy_policy
* Facebook:
https://www.facebook.com/policies_center
* Twitter:
https://twitter.com/privacy
